{"tid":1835191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求所有賣假口罩淘寶口罩嘅藥房馬上下架，香港人咪撚再幫襯。","createTime":"2020-01-22T17:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T18:15:06.000Z","uid":288648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"785dfd79266357075dbe11fe235048b741e97516","tid":1835191,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 ，賣埋曬啲假醫療用品，到時搞出人命點撚算？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家呼籲所有藥房， 馬上下架所有已知嘅假貨！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n如果唔係香港人將你地永久blacklist，係你地門口貼大poster，屌柒你地賣假野。<br />\n<br />\n咪撚喺藥房買呢種包裝既口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1834258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1834258</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇下隔離post有幾多個人中招<br />\n啲藥房明顯明知係假嘅都照扮日本野賣<br />\n賣假嘢都算 仲要mark個價錢咁撚貴<br />\n屌你老母 入貨2.5蚊一盒 賣到60 70蚊<br />\n一盒口罩賺67.5蚊？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRkXuAF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRkXuAF.jpg&h=02207d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家唔好再買啦！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班仆街藥房撚發死人財<br />\n有冇良心呀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"e97bb6f23561f40d832031452629c263230fd78e","tid":1835191,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"cc24856ad1cf94c50dcd3b432ed023aef3abbe3c","tid":1835191,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:00:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老豆"},{"pid":"8e4921e9d22086ec5357d9bf3a5a3413905ddafc","tid":1835191,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"屌你全家"},{"pid":"72a844178126d3eba3ee947032258c568440e2d0","tid":1835191,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"祝賣假野嘅藥房撚中肺炎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\